Package: bre
Title: Helper Functions for Blackstone Research and Evaluation
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Zack", "Crowley", , "zcrowley@blackstoneevaluation.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Blackstone Research and Evaluation", role = c("cph", "fnd"))
  )
Description: The goal of `bre` is to make data cleaning and the
    creation of visualizations easier and faster for Blackstone Research and Evaluation.
    `bre` contains functions to create visuals with Blackstone Research and Evaluation
    branding and helper functions for common data cleaning and
    manipulation tasks for everyone at Blackstone Research and Evaluation.
